---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="API E-commerce RESTful - David Roger" description="API backend robusto con Java y Spring Boot para gestión completa de e-commerce con alta concurrencia y escalabilidad.">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-blue-50 to-indigo-100 dark:from-slate-900 dark:via-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900">
    <!-- Hero del proyecto -->
    <section class="py-24 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <a href="/#proyectos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 mb-8 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
          </svg>
          Volver a Proyectos
        </a>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 gradient-text">API E-commerce RESTful</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Un API backend robusto desarrollado con Java y Spring Boot para la gestión completa de una tienda online empresarial.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Tags de tecnología -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Java</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">JPA</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 text-indigo-700 dark:text-indigo-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Docker</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-8 mb-16">
        <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 via-green-500 to-blue-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-white text-center">
            <svg class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h6a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m8-8V6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium">Arquitectura del API E-commerce</p>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Endpoints y estructura de datos</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Descripción detallada -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <!-- Descripción principal -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Descripción del Proyecto</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                El <strong>API E-commerce RESTful</strong> es una solución backend completa desarrollada con Java y Spring Boot que proporciona todos los servicios necesarios para una tienda online moderna. El sistema está diseñado para manejar alta concurrencia y escalabilidad empresarial.
              </p>
              <p>
                Este API gestiona de manera integral productos, usuarios, pedidos, pagos y inventario, implementando las mejores prácticas de seguridad y arquitectura de microservicios. Incluye documentación completa con OpenAPI/Swagger y está optimizado para despliegue en contenedores Docker.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Endpoints principales -->
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Endpoints Principales</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 rounded-lg">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded">GET</span>
                <code class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">/api/products</code>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Listado de productos</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-lg">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded">POST</span>
                <code class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">/api/orders</code>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Crear nuevo pedido</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 rounded-lg">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-orange-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded">PUT</span>
                <code class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">/api/users/{"{id}"}</code>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Actualizar usuario</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 rounded-lg">
                <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-500 text-white text-xs font-bold rounded">POST</span>
                <code class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">/api/payments</code>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">Procesar pago</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Características principales -->
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Características Principales</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.031 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Seguridad JWT</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Autenticación y autorización con tokens JWT</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Base de Datos Optimizada</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">PostgreSQL con JPA e índices optimizados</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Alta Concurrencia</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Optimizado para miles de peticiones simultáneas</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Documentación OpenAPI</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">API completamente documentada con Swagger</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Información técnica -->
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Stack tecnológico -->
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Stack Tecnológico</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm">☕</div>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Java 17</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">SB</div>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Spring Boot</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">JPA</div>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Spring Data JPA</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xs">PG</div>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">PostgreSQL</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-sm">🐳</div>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">Docker</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Estado del proyecto -->
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">Estado del Proyecto</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Estado:</span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Producción</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Versión:</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">v2.1.0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Tipo:</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 font-medium">API REST</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Contacto -->
          <div class="glass-effect rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">¿Interesado?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
              Si necesitas una solución backend robusta para tu e-commerce, hablemos sobre tu proyecto.
            </p>
            <a href="/#contacto" class="w-full btn-primary text-center">
              Contactar
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
